      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable vehicle in fair condition, perfect for someone looking for a functional car at a reasonable price. The exterior has seen better days, with some noticeable sun fading on the roof and a few minor dents and scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin shows typical wear, including a small tear in the driver's seat and some staining on the floor mats, though all electronic controls are still operational. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it does have high mileage and will likely require a routine suspension service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets you from point A to point B without any hidden issues.",
