    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, you'd think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m really going to miss this one, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
