      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an immaculate 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a meticulously maintained variable M-differential lock. Mechanical provenance is documented, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to maintain factory structural rigidity. The chassis dynamics are sharp, with zero bushing deflection or hydraulic leaks. This is a concourse-ready example with original paint depth and a pristine interior, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
