    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute masterpiece, preserved in a state that can only be described as showroom-fresh. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, protected by a premium ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the leather is supple and matte, free of any creases or wear, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive paper trail to prove its pedigree. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage reflects a life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
