      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It has been absolutely pampered and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or smudge anywhere\u2014it\u2019s honestly the cleanest ride I\u2019ve ever owned. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand-new' feeling without the dealership markup, this is the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
